section_summary: The text is a transcript of a session in the Kuwaiti Parliament, specifically the opening session of the 17th legislative term. The text includes the opening remarks by the President of the Parliament, Mr. Marzouq Al-Hubaini, and the speech of the President of the National Assembly.
